media:group.media:title: What we actually do here | US Digital
media:group.media:description: At US Digital, we’re passionate about manufacturing, automation, robotics and of course designing and making encoders. We create videos to support our customers and celebrate manufacturing and engineering, all while having fun along the way. We're releasing multiple videos each month, so make sure to subscribe to our channel so you don’t miss a thing.
